com.interpss.simu.multicase.rule

Interface BusActionRule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusActionRuleImpl

    public interface BusActionRule
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Bus Action Rule'. Class for defining Bus action rule. Bus rule is evaluated against voltage limit. It has a set of conditions and a set of bus actions, which are BusModification objects. All rule conditions use the same condition operator (AND or OR).

    The following features are supported:

    • Parent
    • Opt Type
    • Bus Condition
    • Bus Action
    See Also:
    MCaseRulePackage.getBusActionRule()
